Hong Kong Government Re-Appoints Eddy Fong as SFC Chairman

-- B y   M a r c o   L u i
-- 
2011-09-29T08:49:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/hong-kong-government-re-appoints-eddy-fong-as-sfc-chairman.html
Hong Kong  re-appointed Eddy Fong as
the chairman of the Securities and Futures Commission for
another year to Oct. 19, 2012, the government said in a
statement on its website today.  Chan Kam-lam and Lawrence Lee Kam-hung were re-appointed as
non-executive directors to the regulator for a term of two
years, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marco Lui at 
 mlui11@bloomberg.net  